summary: OK so i think i made it better this time ;)
descriptionHtml:
I just couldn\'t look at armor i made, so I decided to fix it... its just badly designed so its hard to improve and since i dint want to start over i just put some bump mapping on it along with some \"dirt\" on crystals/glass and golden parts... also changed shoulder guards so they no longer scream kill me...

I give up on that armor...and I hope this one is little better and doesn\'t hurt eyes so much :)
author: bitzupa
